intent.user_query: What are the top 3 states with the most registered customers?

phases.goal: Execute SQL query on fitness_db: SELECT State, COUNT(*) AS NumberOfCustomers FROM fitness_db.Customers GROUP BY State ORDER BY NumberOfCustomers DESC QUALIFY ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY NumberOfCustomers DESC) <= 3;

arguments.sql: SELECT State, COUNT(*) AS NumberOfCustomers FROM fitness_db.Customers GROUP BY State ORDER BY NumberOfCustomers DESC QUALIFY ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY NumberOfCustomers DESC) <= 3;

phases.goal: Generate the final report based on the query results.
